# Memorix Component Guidelines

Use this template when creating new React components for Memorix:

## Component Template
@.cursor/templates/Component.tsx

## Style Guidelines
- Always use Tailwind CSS for styling
- Follow the color scheme defined in rules.json
- Primary accent color: #00ff94
- Dark background: #18092a
- Use responsive design with Tailwind modifiers (sm:, md:, lg:)
- Components should be functional with React hooks
- Organize imports: React first, third-party libraries second, local components last
